# Booking UI

Read **`docs/agents/ui.md`** before non-trivial changes.

- Dashboard: table (default), calendar, and timetable views in `app/page.tsx`; shell in `components/dashboard/*`.
- Create/edit: `components/booking-dialog.tsx` + `components/booking-room-availability-panel.tsx` + `hooks/use-room-availability.ts`.
- Table: server-driven filters/sort/pagination via `hooks/use-bookings-table.ts` and `components/booking-views.tsx`.
- Calendar: vendored `calendar/` + `lib/calendar-mapping.ts`; fetches visible range only.
- Add UI primitives with **`npx shadcn@latest add <name> --yes`** — do not hand-roll `components/ui/*`.
- Date ranges: `components/date-range-picker.tsx` with Calendar `mode="range"` (no shadcn `date-picker` block).
- Room colors: `lib/rooms.ts`.

Match existing Tailwind/shadcn patterns in sibling components.
